Developer information
######################

About this documentation
===================================

How to generate this documentation
-----------------------------------

First, you need to install Sphinx if it is not already installed::

    easy_install -U sphinx

Then, go into the main directory of the source code (e.g., plants/MAppleT), and type::

    python setup.py build_sphinx

or in the ./doc directory, type::

    make html



How to upload it on the web
------------------------------

In the main directory of the source code (vplants/MAppleT), type::

    python setup.py upload_sphinx


